_json.description: One of the most famous Indian rice dishes is the much touted Biryani. A traditional authentic Biryani is made with meat that is marinated in various masalas to make a delish rice mix. Here, we have a lip-smacking variation of the most loved Indian delicacy sans meat for all our vegetarian friends.
